    "description": "这款游戏是《Inn Tycoon》的免费版本.<br><br>与《Inn Tycoon: Prologue》一起踏上一段宁静的中世纪之旅——这是一个塑造昔日宁静的放松游戏。美味佳肴和冰饮等待着您为客人提供服务。通过各种客房选项和定制家具提升声誉。您的梦幻客栈正在等待您来体验这美妙的氛围。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/81546150725a374908428245ea94f60f.poster.avif?t=1729076986\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/81546150725a374908428245ea94f60f.webm?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/81546150725a374908428245ea94f60f.mp4?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招聘员工提供最佳服务</h2><br>招募一支技能娴熟的团队，确保您的客栈运营如行云流水。从厨师和女佣到表演者，每位员工在为客人营造流畅愉悦的住宿体验中扮演着至关重要的角色。您的顾客可能会不耐烦，请小心不要让他们失望。记住，优质服务=丰厚小费。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/bce1472fb526c38303fec71addd66c37.poster.avif?t=1729076986\" width=646 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/bce1472fb526c38303fec71addd66c37.webm?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/bce1472fb526c38303fec71addd66c37.mp4?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >意外的季节变化</h2><br>有时是寒冷多雪的一天，有时是灼热的天气。经常变化的天气也会在客栈内感受到。您需要适应意外情况并处理客户的不同需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/102dfe8be3232e9696219b2549fbc193.poster.avif?t=1729076986\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/102dfe8be3232e9696219b2549fbc193.webm?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064020/extras/102dfe8be3232e9696219b2549fbc193.mp4?t=1729076986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用声望创建节日</h2><br>您将能够利用您所获得的声望组织活动和节庆。在墙壁上回响的音乐和笑声中体验轻松愉快的客栈管理。",
